{"tid":1839154,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[堅持‧承諾] 不分和勇 抗爭融入生活 二百萬人日常活動","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:15:07.000Z","uid":27993,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d62fd5fc9d6a733ecbce47368f2f344ecf0a0d7","tid":1839154,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"之前錯台重開<br />\n<br />\n首先，好重要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚黃大仙/車公廟/維園見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n抗爭沒有降溫，不會停止。每個人都係自己崗位做現時做到既野。如果你覺得靜左，只係你靜左。唔好麻目，諗上自己可以做D咩，可唔可以做多D。<br />\n以下係香港最少想改變嗰200萬人都應該要做既野，而大部份人都冇上LIHKG，所以大家睇完幫手Share出去，俾所有和理非所有手足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 黃色經濟圈 拒絕無良藍店 殺人紅店</span></span><br />\n <br />\n香港人支持黃色經濟圈時應已察覺，要一下子謝絕所有紅藍資本，好影響生活。<br />\n怕麻煩？已經有人擁抱更多麻煩，做左一系列既APP/ TG Channel，再整合做文宣方便你，請你Save左張圖，然後Add to favorite<br />\n堅持黃色經濟圈。生活習慣都改變唔到，談反抗？復仇？光復香港？<br />\n200萬人當中，一定有一班人因為麻煩，而忽視依樣野。既然不能一步到位，最少要循序漸進，先抵制藍紅大企業大集團，集中火力，逐一擊破<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支持黃色經濟圈，最簡單由飲食開始。最少裝WhatsGap，和你Eat等等。一打開就有地圖，冇心機搵黃店至少唔好入藍店！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. $1和你交</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除咗稅之外，但凡關於港共既繳款，水費grantloan，請堅持$1交。</span><br />\n攻略：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1811809/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1811809/page/1</a><br />\n當$1交錢出現既時間，港共有相應措施，限制每日交易次數，令$1交錢門檻上升。<br />\n記住，不論所有抗爭行為，對方一定有反制措施，依個時間要做既，唔係話依招冇用咁樣唔Work<br />\n而係要因應佢既反制措施再諗行動。<br />\n如果因為門檻高左而放棄，麻煩左而唔去做，咁樣每個抗爭行為都一定唔會有用。<br />\n因應佢既措施，我自己開多左3個銀行Account，冇IT背景上網自學Python，寫左4個Prog，每個銀行每日交$50，5日就可以交$1000，20個工作天可以交$4000 (仲有個別銀行係冇限制架)<br />\n如是者我每個月既電子月結單係80頁既$1<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">面對極權阻撓，我地要做既係堅持，反抗，絕對唔係放棄！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. Twitter Reddit 聯署 國際戰線</span></span><br />\nTwitter TG Bot: <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77fzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=5959954e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n聯署Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77fzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ee9f5008\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg</a><br />\n聯署機攻略: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1827349/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1827349/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 聯署係最容易，小朋友都做到既野，<span style=\"color: red;\">每日抽少少時間，禁兩個掣。</span><br />\n同樣地，有手足已經將好麻煩既野自己做曬，為既係令大家可以更方便，希望大家可以一齊堅持落去。<br />\n聯署Channel只要有10萬人，而入左去既人每次都簽名，基本上聯署一出，就可以夠人。當然10萬係唔夠，愈多愈好。<br />\n<br />\n比較難做既係，支共已經有大量網軍係唔同平台抹黑香港人<br />\n大家可以係Reddit Twitter幫手解話反抹黑，俾更多外國人知道真相。<br />\n如果失敗，共產黨最後一步係抹殺香港人，共產黨一定會咁做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. 文宣 日程 快閃連儂開花</span></span><br />\n快閃連儂開花: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1819022/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1819022/page/1</a><br />\n文宣集合TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77fzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=00aa7630\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n每個地方都係連儂牆，有攻略有教學。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要快推日程！</span><br />\n平時可以幫手Share多D文宣 日程 Airdrop又好 諗到既都去做<br />\n要知道依加班狗追住文宣組，連儂手咬，亦有好多人被票控<br />\n唔好再期待其他人去幫你做你應該做既野啦<br />\n<br />\n煲底見！"},{"pid":"1cb88eb99116d6dcae3db0781d0813fe0cecaea7","tid":1839154,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:52:42.000Z","msg":"香港人 煲底見！"},{"pid":"4c47d1f49a3d11ba0b44a5d9ff1e2f8554ad71d7","tid":1839154,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c8f547018c683b082418084d922490b9796661ce","tid":1839154,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f0882c731d66dc1313819aa364e1cf1aefd23dc","tid":1839154,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0571b8cb7f27a52c356e4d0fc23a66e9e22edd37","tid":1839154,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153b9bb7c65f291baf46b6877f2b4eeb430c3081","tid":1839154,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936750d3c43c28e60bdb1df7239607cf98560d18","tid":1839154,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c84faa432e4ed852333a2ca60a424c2281f7d7","tid":1839154,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e261930bba7673ecbc619af9f60a6a5e245a8d4f","tid":1839154,"uid":236957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"支持！去撐黃店嗰陣順便幫佢哋登記飲食界！<br />\n<br />\n